PhyUorrhina /uliginosa Temminck, 1853, 
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3753598342" pageId="21" pageNumber="248">
“La côte de 
<collectingCountry box="[1528,1644,2767,2806]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="21" pageNumber="248">Guiné</collectingCountry>
